author: Football Italia staff
title: Cellino: 'Found COVID-19 in blood test'
description: Brescia President Massimo Cellino reveals he tested negative for COVID-19 on a swab, but a blood test found he was positive. “I was only having the test to end the quarantine.”
content:
Brescia President Massimo Cellino reveals he tested negative for COVID-19 on a swab, but a blood test found he was positive. “I was only having the test to end the quarantine.”
